        <p>I'm Eric, a full-stack engineer on the International team at <a href="https://www.udacity.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Udacity</a>. My day-to-day consists of writing software and making data-informed decisions to ensure access to high-quality educational experiences for people all over the world.</p>
