        <p>During my time at Cornell, I served as the Creative Director for <a href="https://cusd.cornell.edu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cornell University Sustainable Design (CUSD)</a>, a 150+ student organization that specializes in sustainable architecture. I also helped manage a student co-working space called POPSHOP and founded <a href="https://yorango.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yorango</a>, a real-estate startup that focuses on student rentals and subleases.</p>
